PrecisAppointment of WILLIAM GRANT HINCHEY, of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Northwest Territories, as a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of David A. Ordish, whose term has expired.
